<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16679153264172836120">Elmore John Leonard lived in Dallas, Oklahoma City and Memphis before settling in Detroit in 1935. After serving in the navy, he studied English literature at the University of Detroit where he entered a short story competition. His earliest published novels in the 1950s were westerns, but Leonard went on to specialize in crime fiction and suspense thrillers, many of which have been adapted into m</span>
  <span id="freeText16679153264172836120" style="display:none">Elmore John Leonard lived in Dallas, Oklahoma City and Memphis before settling in Detroit in 1935. After serving in the navy, he studied English literature at the University of Detroit where he entered a short story competition. His earliest published novels in the 1950s were westerns, but Leonard went on to specialize in crime fiction and suspense thrillers, many of which have been adapted into motion pictures.<br /><br />Father of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/220840.Peter_Leonard" title="Peter Leonard" rel="nofollow noopener">Peter Leonard</a>.</span>
